Pat Musick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Musick 0 Patrice Anne Musick (born January 26, 1956) is an American voice actress, who has provided numerous voices in many television shows, films and video games. She and her former husband Jeff Whitman, a personal manager and set construction coordinator, are the parents of actress and singer Mae Whitman.
